ct and mutual understanding"--cProvided by publisher.0 aVendor-supplied metadata.  a44 0aMulticultural educationzKorea (South) 0aImmigrantsxEducationzKorea (South) 0aEducation and statezKorea (South) 0aRoutledge critical studies in Asian education.403University of Alberta Accessuhttp://search.ebscohost.com/login.aspx?direct=true&scope=site&db=nlebk&db=nlabk&AN=905749z(Single User Access)  hUAINzPDAOWNED  aInternet AccesswLCc1i6774785-1001lINTERNETmUAINTERNETrYsYtE-RESOURCEu1/13/2015xE-BOOKzPDAOWNED01ahttp://id.loc.gov/authorities/names/n2008009999bhttp://viaf.org/viaf/315983701